3. cs.Distributed - The paper's focus on distributed systems and the use of atomic registers suggests that it may fall under the distributed computing sub-category. 
4. cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) - The paper may involve logical reasoning and analysis in the design and implementation of timestamp systems.
